 Privacy Policy for RU Movies Info

Last Updated: May 5, 2026

1. Introduction
Welcome to RU Movies Info. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our application.

2. Data Collection and Usage
RU Movies Info does not collect, store, or share any personal data or personally identifiable information (PII). We do not require you to create an account, log in, or provide any personal details to use the app.

3. Local Storage
The application stores certain data locally on your device to improve your experience:
- Favorites: Movies and TV shows you mark as favorites are saved in a local database on your device.
- Preferences: Your settings, such as your preferred theme (Dark/Light mode) and watch provider region, are stored locally.
This data never leaves your device and is not sent to any external servers by us.

4. Third-Party Services
Our application uses the TMDB (The Movie Database) API to display movie and television data, images, and watch provider information. 
- When the app fetches data, it makes network requests to TMDB's servers. 
- Please note that TMDB may collect standard network information (like IP addresses) as part of normal internet operations. You can review TMDB's privacy policy on their official website (https://www.themoviedb.org/privacy-policy) for more details.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Since we do not collect contact information, we cannot notify you directly of changes. Any updates will be reflected in this document within the app.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, please feel free to reach out to the developer at:
